Definitions.Name: DeleteObsoleteAnnotation
Definitions.Message: '{0:scanTarget}' contains a use of the obsolete or redundant '{1:obsoleteAnnotation}' annotation that should be removed.

Definitions.Name: ReplaceObsoleteAnnotation
Definitions.Message: '{0:scanTarget}' contains a use of the obsolete or redundant '{1:obsoleteAnnotation}' annotation and should be replaced for '{2:newAnnotation}'.
Definitions.Description: SAL 1 can be replaced with SAL 2.

updateAnnotation.Description: Replace '[returnvalue: SA_Post( Deref=(1), Null=SA_Yes, NullTerminated=SA_No )]' for '_At_(*return, _Ret_null_ _Ret1_impl_(__notzterm_impl))'.

Definitions.Name: ConvertObsoleteAnnotation
Definitions.Message: '{0:scanTarget}' contains a use of the SAL v1 '{1:obsoleteAnnotation} annotation that should be converted manually to the correct SAL v2 pattern.
Definitions.Description: Conversion from SAL 1 to SAL 2 cannot be automatically done.
